<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 huí shǒu zài huí shǒu kàn kàn nǐ zǒu guò de lù
 duō shǎo fèng xiàn duō shǎo fù chū guāng yīn shì fǒu xū dù
 lí kāi jiā mén de shí hòu jué zhì yào gēn zhǔ zǒu
 hái yǒu jǐ fēn liú liàn de nǐ jīn tiān shì fǒu chéng shú
 zhī dào méi yǒu tǎn tú zhī dào duō yǒu duì fù
 yě yǒu chóu chú shāng xīn de shí hòu dàn nǐ méi yǒu huí tóu
 wǒ men tóng zǒu yī tiáo lù wǒ men zǒu guò yī dào dào gōu
 zài méi yǒu liú làng de bèi yǐng yào bǎ líng hún zhěng jiù.</lyrics>
<title>huí shǒu zài huí shǒu 迦南219</title>
<hymn_number>219</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>